+    // COMPANION (OpenMW-DS): the single container/loot/pickpocket window instance (WindowManager owns
+    // exactly one, for its whole lifetime), captured in the ctor. Lets the DS take path
+    // (companion_global.lua) route a pickpocket take through the REAL native item model -- see
